verbose_text: These data suggest that cisplatin had cytotoxicity in NRK-52E cells, influencing both cell viability and cell apoptosis, and that inhibiting miR-449 promoted cell viability and suppressed cell apoptosis, which might protect NRK-52E cells from cisplatin induced renal tubular cell injury.
evidence: apoptosis, which might protect NRK-52E cells from cisplatin-induced renal tubular cell injury
